# REQUIREMENTS PHASE

## Project Requirement
Requirements: Create a requirements document for a simple to-do list application with the following features:

1. User Authentication
2. Task Management (Create, Read, Update, Delete)
3. Task Categories/Labels
4. Due Dates and Reminders
5. Task Priority Levels
6. Search and Filter capabilities

Assigned Team: ai-business-analyst
Executor AI: ai-business-analyst

## Phase Objective
Analyze and document project requirements.
